{"tid":2014114,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人間唔中會有種自己已經死咗嘅感覺","createTime":"2020-05-12T20:02:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T22:07:38.000Z","uid":138740,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"490b8eca357683ed22e2ae6c75e211b6bda8983a","tid":2014114,"uid":138740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T20:02:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />利申先 嗱我就無諗住自殺嘅<br />\n如果我無啦啦死鳩咗，一定唔係自殺<br />\n<br />\n雖然年紀唔係好大<br />\n但試過幾次有種自己已經死咗嘅feel<br />\n會覺得依家嘅「我」同以前唔同階段嘅「我」係唔同人嚟<br />\n<br />\n唔知有無人明我講咩<br />\n唔係因為情緒低落<br />\n突然無原因地出現依個感覺<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪精神問題嚟"},{"pid":"70c9ed928f4f095751af35aca3ea93a720d6f09f","tid":2014114,"uid":321400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T20:05:14.000Z","msg":"唔係"},{"pid":"7ee330b25e543f7a5ad7b6a058ca51510e016186","tid":2014114,"uid":61084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T20:53:52.000Z","msg":"重生咗。"},{"pid":"91641097b9d9a4b3439d25a50337b1708d513e8a","tid":2014114,"uid":138740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ee330b25e543f7a5ad7b6a058ca51510e016186","tid":2014114,"uid":61084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T20:53:52.000Z","msg":"重生咗。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T21:55:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係就好喇"},{"pid":"120f7b429ade01381863580607712f2ae8e346f2","tid":2014114,"uid":316610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T22:16:59.000Z","msg":"我明你"},{"pid":"ddb8b690015d47de601dac77564d899e9016408d","tid":2014114,"uid":138740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"120f7b429ade01381863580607712f2ae8e346f2","tid":2014114,"uid":316610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T22:16:59.000Z","msg":"我明你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T05:22:44.000Z","msg":"咁你知唔知點解會咁"},{"pid":"be426594